| Feature | Framerecall | Vector DBs | Traditional DBs |
|---------|--------|------------|-----------------|
| Storage Efficiency | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ | ⭐⭐ | ⭐⭐⭐ |
| Setup Complexity | Simple | Complex | Complex |
| Semantic Search | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Offline Usage | ✅ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Portability | File-based | Server-based | Server-based |
| Scalability | Millions | Millions | Billions |
| Cost | Free | $$$$ | $$$ |



